Exercises.Name: Ashys Dynamic Warm Up
Tips: Aim to feel warm, loose and ready to exercise after this warm up.
If you find you require a little longer to warm up, do 2 to 4 minutes gentle cardio prior to this dynamic warm up
Instructions: Perform the reps for each exercise 1 after the other until completed

Exercises.Name: Smith Squat
Instructions: Bring feet out further than you normally would, so you can feel your gluts and hammys and your spine can remain neutral during the lift.
Move your feet around until you feel comfortable.
Your spine should be as vertical as possible.
